{"tid":1633292,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以慢制快，政府越急我地越要慢慢黎","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T11:23:32.000Z","uid":119525,"like":54,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"94a46e5cecb2943871b8cfcd464476c1ab88ffbd","tid":1633292,"uid":119525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"政府而家已經急到係咁要係連登帶風叫人日日出黎，佢咁急我地就應該反其道而行慢慢拖。<br />\n<br />\n首先美國民主及人權法案月中就會上兩院，過左就可以制裁港共狗官同中聯港奧辦，咁先係對佢地最痛既手段，同時比到個訊息歐洲個邊跟機。<br />\n<br />\n二黎你黨鐵中資葵心360本身已經裝修左，佢都未整返好今日再好裝都根本就冇意思。<br />\n<br />\n三黎拖到區議會佢用緊急法cancel又死唔取消又死。<br />\n<br />\n大家要明白時間係我地既朋友，只係政府先急緊要點處理好。往後戰術可以1日十八區就咩都好1日爆買黃鋪日，人地咁撐我地我地係咪應該set日支持返。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"00ef7f0123311d0c12eb340b6495cb0d9b88cdeb","tid":1633292,"uid":150315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:20:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"337b62cd2884983d94b61c1a05780a58c801b48b","tid":1633292,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:20:39.000Z","msg":"「認真」各位手足 借東風啊！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c426123952d63ed0c2511f5620fa0c44540a888a","tid":1633292,"uid":96814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:20:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b3c6a279f63f66defd1f25f4341073b74fd11302","tid":1633292,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:21:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c2a420c84a373560d9e7c82cd1bc1b2f70b1634","tid":1633292,"uid":119525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:23:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f1e1edac90f509db25b1d124078067e3e97c39b0","tid":1633292,"uid":119525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:36:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eb14624f6565a0850e51e850aceebc3205387c96","tid":1633292,"uid":5936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019